OL,3,CFire service records 'busiest week' in
OL,4,Cnearly four years
OL,6,FDevon and Somerset Fire and Rescue
OL,7,FService (DSFRS) is warning people
OL,8,Fabout the high risk of wildfires as
OL,9,Fthe hot weather continues, after
OL,10,Frecording its busiest week in nearly
OL,11,Ffour years.
OL,13,FThe fire service said crews attended
OL,14,F813 incidents in the week from 9 to 16
OL,15,FJuly, including 226 fires - an average
OL,16,Fof one incident every 12 minutes.
OL,18,FThe fire control room received nearly
OL,19,F2000 calls in the same period.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
