OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1784621897
OL,3,CFire service records 'busiest week' in
OL,4,Cnearly four years
OL,6,FDSFRS is warning people that the risk
OL,7,Fof fire remains high, and small fires
OL,8,Fcan spread quickly.
OL,10,FShortly after 5pm yesterday evening
OL,11,F(17 July), fire crews from Taunton,
OL,12,FBridgwater, Chard, and Wellington were
OL,13,Fcalled to tackle a large fire in a
OL,14,Fcrop field near Taunton.
OL,16,FFive pumps were used to extinguish the
OL,17,Fblaze, which is no longer ongoing.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1784621897
OL,3,CFire service records 'busiest week' in
OL,4,Cnearly four years
OL,6,FMeanwhile, a fire involving 200 tonnes
OL,7,Fof woodchip broke out on Ilminster
OL,8,FRoad just off the A358, near Taunton,
OL,9,Fearlier this week (16 July).
OL,11,FAt its height, four fire engines and a
OL,12,Fwater bowser were at the scene of the
OL,13,Ffire, the fire service said.
OL,15,FA spokesperson for DSFRS said: "With
OL,16,Fthe hot weather and dry ground
OL,17,Fcontinuing this weekend, the risk of
OL,18,Ffire remains high.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1784621898
OL,3,CFire service records 'busiest week' in
OL,4,Cnearly four years
OL,6,F"Small fires can spread quickly,
OL,7,Fturning a car fire into a large
OL,8,Fhedgerow fire, or an unattended BBQ or
OL,9,Fbonfire into a wildfire covering acres
OL,10,Fof land.
OL,12,F"We've also seen an increase in calls
OL,13,Fto help the ambulance service gain
OL,14,Fentry to properties as the heat
OL,15,Faffects some of the most vulnerable in
OL,16,Four communities. Please take a moment
OL,17,Fto check on family, friends and
OL,18,Fneighbours.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
