PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1784621898
OL,3,CFire service records 'busiest week' in
OL,4,Cnearly four years
OL,6,F"A huge thank you to all of our
OL,7,Fcolleagues, on the frontline and
OL,8,Fbehind the scenes, who continue to
OL,9,Fwork tirelessly to keep our
OL,10,Fcommunities safe during this
OL,11,Fexceptionally busy period."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
